      "message": "Patch Set 11: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nAside from fixing the cache, I wonder why put all of this complexity in the kernel?\n\nCannot we just extend lctl set_param to fork N-way and write the requested value in all found files in parallel?\n\nThe added benefit is that we'll automatically gain this support for all the other controls that might benefit from it.",
